  ⚠ `conda-pypi-map = {}` is deprecated
  help: Use `conda-pypi-map = false` to disable all PyPI name derivation, or `conda-pypi-map = { conda-forge = { mapping-mode = "replace" } }` to avoid default mapping lookups while keeping the
        conda-forge same-name heuristic.
